'}How It's Made{'

'}

Hi, my name is Carlos Carrasquillo, and this is my first attempt at a website! This page is dedicated to breaking down the creative and technical processes that went into designing and coding up what you see.

All in all, this was a highly valuable learning experience for me. I want others to benefit from the this little experiment as well, so I have included the source code to this website below. I have also included a list of bugs at the end of this page. If anyone finds a new bug and/or a bug-fix, please email me personally or via the contact form on the Contact Me page.

Thank you for checking out my site! Follow me on GitHub for more small-scale projects.
